      "acceptanceCriteria": "Equivalency between simulation input parameters and physical test conditions must be evaluated.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, detailed equivalency mapping is not required beyond confirmation that boundary conditions match the experimental setup. This confirmation was performed qualitatively. No further assessment is required at this model risk level."
