    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied at all five COU operating points.",
